y 2nd Bn-377th Arty Reg Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry Division]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team's]], [[377th Field Artillery Regiment]], 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:82nd Airborne Division Artillery Beret Flash.svg|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division Artillery|82nd Airborne (ABN) Division (Div) Artillery (ARTY)]]</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div ARTY's [[319th Field Artillery Regiment|319th Field ARTY Regiment]], [[1st Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|1st Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div ARTY's 319th Field ARTY Regiment, [[2nd Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|2nd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 3rd BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN Div ARTY's 319th Field ARTY Regiment, [[3rd Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|3rd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 4th BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd ABN Brigade's]] 319th Field ARTY Regiment, [[4th Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|4th Battalion]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Infantry Branch (United States)|Infantry]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:75thrangerflash.svg|<center>[[United States Army Special Operations Command|US Army Special Operations Command]]'s (USASOC) [[75th Ranger Regiment (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment]] and [[Special Troops Battalion]]</center>\nFile:1 Bn 75 Ranger Regiment Beret Flash.svg|<center>USASOC's [[1st Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 1st Battalion]]</center>\nFile:Image5435.gif|<center>USASOC's [[2nd Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 2nd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:Image5436.gif|<center>USASOC's [[3rd Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 3rd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 4th Bde-25th ID Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Divisi